-- CANADA RESEARCH ROUNDUP-Kirkland Lake, Transforce 
-- 
-- Tue Apr 15, 2014 05:42AM EDT
-- None



April 15 (Reuters) - Securities analysts revised their ratings and price targets on several Canadian companies, including Transforce and Kirkland Lake, on Tuesday.

HIGHLIGHTS * Kirkland Lake <KGI.TO> : CIBC cuts to sector underperformer rating * Transforce <TFI.TO>: Canaccord Genuity starts with target price of C$29  Following is a summary of research actions on Canadian companies reported by Reuters on Tuesday. Stock entries are in alphabetical order.* Amica Mature Lifestyles <ACC.TO>: Canaccord Genuity cuts target to C$9.40; rating buy * Amica Mature Lifestyles <ACC.TO>: NBF cuts target to C$9.50 from C$10; rating outperform * Crescent Point Energy <CPG.TO>: Canaccord Genuity raises target price to C$50; rating buy * Crescent Point Energy <CPG.TO>: NBF raises target to C$52 from C$51; rating outperform * Kirkland Lake <KGI.TO> : CIBC cuts to sector underperformer rating * RMP Energy <RMP.TO>: CIBC cuts to sector performer from sector outperformer * Sirius XM Canada Holdings <XSR.TO>: Canaccord Genuity cuts target to C$8.90; rating buy * Sirius XM Canada Holdings <XSR.TO>: NBF cuts target price to C$11 from C$11.50; outperform * Torc Oil & Gas Ltd <TOG.TO>: Canaccord Genuity raises target price to C$15; rating buy * Transforce <TFI.TO>: Canaccord Genuity starts with target price of C$29